div.p:
Ten minutes later BGSBrigadier General
                                Staff (Jasper G. Frere). Ninth Army telephoned me “French are

 shelling Damascus;
                            General Pilleau will see General HumblotGen. Emile Humblot, Commander of French forces in Syria and
                                Lebanon. at once; I am off for Damascus; can’t dine with you;
                            good-by”.
